---
title: Lemony Shrimp Linguine with Roasted Red Pepper, Garlic, and Chili
description: Lemon, butter, and shrimp is one of our all-time favorite combinations. Amped up by garlic and spicy chili flakes, this is a dish made great by its simplicity. The addition of caramelized bell pepper adds a nice touch of sweetness. If your kids don’t like spicy, simply add the chili flakes to the adult plates at the end!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemony-shrimp-linguine-8b4567.jpg
